    "moments": [
      {
        "id": "mo_001",
        "text": "I love when a match ends with a tight finish, like a last-ball win. It gives me adrenaline.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_002",
        "text": "I remember one match where India chased 300 in the last over with friends, we were all shouting. It's moments like that.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_003",
        "text": "The 2004 semi-final between India and Sri Lanka (event), Sri Lanka won with last ball. Dil Chahta Hai (movie) is another special one. Both are special because they're underdog stories.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_004",
        "text": "A friend recommended Dil Chahta Hai (movie). He said it's different. I watched it and really connected with the characters. It was not like other movies I was used to. From that day, it became my favorite.",
        "tone": "grateful",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_005",
        "text": "The 2018 IPL final between Chennai Super Kings and Mumbai Indians (event) was epic. Rain, a tie, and a super over — still gives me chills. The final moments of the super over, Jadhav running between the wickets, that catch by Krunal, it was *dhamaal*. I still remember the tension.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_006",
        "text": "The 2017 Champions Trophy semi-final (event) against Pakistan was memorable because of the teamwork and belief. Even when the target looked big, no one gave up. MS Dhoni (person)'s calm and the way the lower order batted showed India could win under pressure. It felt like a turning point for the team and made me want to follow cricket even more.",
        "tone": "proud",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_007",
        "text": "Last weekend, I played gully cricket with friends. I hit the ball straight and it crashed into the stumps. We all jumped up — priceless moment. Even though we're all in our 30s, it felt like old times.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_008",
        "text": "We went to a small diner after the match and ordered chaat and cold drinks. It's our usual post-match routine. We laughed a lot, replayed the moments — especially my 'stump crasher'. Simple, but perfect.",
        "tone": "content",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_009",
        "text": "The mix of tangy tamarind water, spicy chaat masala, and cool yogurt — dahi puri just hits right after a hot game. Simple, but so satisfying.",
        "tone": "content",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_010",
        "text": "The CSK vs GT 2023 final (event) was intense, a real thriller.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_011",
        "text": "Rajasthan Royals' 2022 comeback (event) was something special, an underdog story.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_012",
        "text": "Gujarat Titans' first win in 2022 (event) was unforgettable — finally breaking CSK and Rajasthan dominance.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_013",
        "text": "The MI vs CSK 2023 qualifier (event), where Faf du Plessis hit a six to win — unbelievable! I rewatch it sometimes and it still gives me adrenaline.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_014",
        "text": "The RCB vs KKR 2023 qualifier (event) was wild. Maxwell's hitting, Pollard's sixes — it was like a party, pure *dhamaal*.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_015",
        "text": "Virat's 12th Man story (event) gets me emotional. It still makes me tear up. Something about the raw realness of it.",
        "tone": "hopeful",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_016",
        "text": "The 2023 Rajasthan qualifier (event) against PBKS, where they chased 200+ — that hit close to home. Felt like my heart was in my throat. Stoinis' finish was absolute *maa chella*.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_017",
        "text": "The 2020 Mumbai vs Delhi qualifier (event) was something else, like a dream. Suryakumar's knock, Tewatia's finish — unforgettable.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_018",
        "text": "The 2020 IPL final (event) was *unbeleivable* — Virat's 100, CSK's chase, still *jaw-dropping*.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_019",
        "text": "The 2019 World Cup semi-final (event) between India and New Zealand was *unforgettable* — that tie, the Super Over. *Naa hoga* but it happened! Watching with friends, we were *all in shock*. Conway's (person) catch? *I still can't believe it!* The drama and tension felt like a movie scene.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_020",
        "text": "The 2016 T20 World Cup final (event) between England and Australia had that *movie moment* feel—rain delay, Duckworth-Lewis, last-over *chaos*. I was *on the edge* the whole time. Five runs off two balls, the tension *unreal*. I was *sweating* like it was my own team. When they won, it felt *so cinematic*.",
        "tone": "excited",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      }
